{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843513033,"sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","part":{"id":"prt_d7885929f001d7ETXW4Z2cLFyk","messageID":"msg_d78856497001gLOBsCVc5qpLgs","sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6b9d33cf6e4943e1a1ae672d0560ab00","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md","limit":50,"offset":590},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n590: \n591: ## 与 client-go 的集成\n592: \n593: 本处理器使用 `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` 中的以下组件，该库为 API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`** 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端代码。\n594: \n595: ### Clientset 结构\n596: \n597: **Interface** (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`):\n598: \n599: ```go\n600: type Interface interface {\n601:     Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n602:     RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n603: }\n604: ```\n605: \n606: **Clientset 构造器**:\n607: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n608: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n609: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\n610: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n611: \n612: ### Typed Client — runtime/v1alpha1\n613: \n614: **RuntimeV1alpha1Interface**:\n615: \n616: ```go\n617: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n618:     RESTClient() rest.Interface\n619:     AgentRuntimesGetter\n620:     CodeInterpretersGetter\n621: }\n622: ```\n623: \n624: **AgentRuntimeInterface**:\n625: ```go\n626: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n627:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n628:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n629:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n630:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n631:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n632:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n633:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n634:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n635:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n636:     AgentRuntimeExpansion\n637: }\n638: ```\n639: \n\n(Showing lines 590-639 of 788. Use offset=640 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n## 与 client-go 的集成\n\n本处理器使用 `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` 中的以下组件，该库为 API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`** 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端代码。\n\n### Clientset 结构\n\n**Interface** (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`):\n\n```go\ntype Interface interface {\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n    RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n}\n```\n\n**Clientset 构造器**:\n- `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n- `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n- `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md","time":{"start":1775843513009,"end":17758435130