{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843525589,"sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","part":{"id":"prt_d7885bf8f001APmpIDIi4p7V56","messageID":"msg_d788593010011ulhtpZ107weFN","sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-1183422ad356465f87e57ffa072543d6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"wc -l /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md","description":"Count total lines in updated design file"},"output":"788 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md\n","metadata":{"output":"788 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md\n","exit":0,"description":"Count total lines in updated design file","truncated":false},"title":"Count total lines in updated design file","time":{"start":1775843525569,"end":1775843525588}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843525596,"sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","part":{"id":"prt_d7885c3a4001pM4exs6Q5Sh5f5","messageID":"msg_d788593010011ulhtpZ107weFN","sessionID":"ses_2877bbc95ffeboA37Xvy0XjYsF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f5e8dd057ef0492c8ba8e48817953431","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md","limit":50,"offset":740},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n740: - `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\")` → `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()`\n741: - `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\")` → `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()`\n742: \n743: ### Scheme 注册\n744: \n745: **文件**: `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n746: \n747: ```go\n748: // AddToScheme 注册 runtime/v1alpha1 类型到 scheme\n749: func AddToScheme(scheme *runtime.Scheme) error {\n750:     return metav1.AddMetaToScheme(scheme)\n751: }\n752: ```\n753: \n754: ### Fake Clients\n755: \n756: 用于单元测试:\n757: - `fake_runtime_client.go` - Fake runtime group client\n758: - `fake_agentruntime.go` - Fake AgentRuntime client\n759: - `fake_codeinterpreter.go` - Fake CodeInterpreter client\n760: \n761: ### 代码生成\n762: \n763: **命令**: `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n764: \n765: **版本**: `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1, `--with-watch`\n766: \n767: **输出包**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n768: \n769: ## 关键决策\n770: \n771: ### 为什么使用 dynamic client 创建 Sandbox 而非 typed client\n772: \n773: Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 是外部 CRD（`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox`），不在 agentcube 的 client-go 生成范围内。使用 `dynamic.Interface` + `unstructured.Unstructured` 是操作未知 schema CRD 的标准做法。\n774: \n775: ### 为什么 Watcher 注册在 CR 创建之前\n776: \n777: 存在竞态条件：如果先创建 CR 再注册 watcher，Sandbox 可能在 watcher 注册前就进入 running 状态，导致永久等待。因此必须先 `WatchSandboxOnce` 注册 channel，再创建 CR。\n778: \n779: ### 为什么需要 Store 占位记录\n780: \n781: 在等待 Sandbox running 期间（最长 2 分钟），Store 中已有记录可以：\n782: 1. 防止重复创建（幂等性检查）\n783: 2. 让 GC 感知到进行中的创建操作\n784: 3. 提供创建失败时的回滚目标\n785: \n786: ### 超时回滚策略\n787: \n788: 2 分钟超时是 spec 规定的硬性要求。超时后必须删除已创建的 CR，否则会产生孤儿 Sandbox 资源。删除操作使用独立的 30 秒 timeout context，避免因删除失败阻塞响应。\n\n(End of file - total 788 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"- `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\")` → `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()`\n- `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\")` → `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()`\n\n### Scheme 注册\n\n**文件**: `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n\n```go\n// AddToScheme 注册 runtime/v1alpha1 类型到 scheme\nfunc AddToScheme(scheme *runtime.Scheme) error {\n    return metav1.AddMetaToScheme(scheme)\n}\n```\n\n### Fake Clients\n\n用于单元测试:\n- `fake_runtime_client.go` - Fake runtime group client\n- `fake_agentruntime.go` - Fake AgentRuntime client\n- `fake_codeinterpreter.go` - Fake CodeInterpreter client","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md","time":{"start":1775843525574,"end":1775843525594}}}}
